<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.10">
<l>ālu māvala vaṉkali kaṉṟi maṅkai yartalai vaṉaṇi poḻil</l>
<l>cēlkaḷ pāykaḻa ṉittiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉai,</l>
<l>nīla māmukil vaṇṇaṉai neṭu mālai yiṉtami ḻālniṉain tavin</l>
<l>nālu māṟumval lārkkiṭa mākumvā ṉulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master these sweet four-and six [songs]</l>
<l rend="indent">which the leader of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l>The one skilled with prancing horses, Kalikaṉṟi conceived with sweet Tamil</l>
<l>About the huge, dark cloud-hued one, tall Māl,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one of Tirukkōṭṭiyūr with beautiful groves</l>
<l>And where carp jump in flooded fields, [their] place will be the heavenly world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
